{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC08_HAR_530.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x19,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Ayesha, get over here!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Okay. Did you find something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhm, you'll know once you see it.<CR>See that!? Isn't it amazing!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Wow...there's a fire burning inside the glass..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Seeing that, doesn't it make you feel that this ruin is still alive?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "This ruin...alive?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. Generally speaking, there are ruins that are dead, and ruins that are alive."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "So this is one of the live ones."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "A forge in a ruin made of glass...<CR>And the glass flowers..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "It's not something I know for a fact, but I feel like it's gotta be related to Nio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x161,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Okay. I'm sure I'll be able to see Nio someday if I continue to search ruins like this one!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Yup. I'll help you, too. If it's about the ruins, leave it to me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, and I need to learn more about the ruins, too!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "So, what is...this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Beats me. I only know that it's something that was made a looong time ago."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Whether this was a temple to worship the gods or a factory to make something..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I have no clue. But the ancient civilization was amazing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure Harry will be satisfied after reporting to him what we saw here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Oh, if you're going back, you should take a souvenir for Harry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "A souvenir? I wonder what I should take back..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Anything will do for Harry. Let's see...maybe this stick thingy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "It has interesting patterns on it...but it's still just a stick..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "It'll be enough. And just tell him what you found at the ruin, and he'll be happy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "It's okay, Harry's extremely fond of things like this anyway."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Then, I'll take this stick as a souvenir. Regina, thank you so much."
        }
    ]
}